    <div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-8 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Importing excise goods to the UK from the EU from 1 January 2021
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">From 1 January 2021, there will be changes to how you import and declare excise goods (alcohol, tobacco and certain oils). </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
